{
  "stem": "10572.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father said to him, no, he wouldn't.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father-- that was his house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he would sell it to our next door neighbor, Dr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Claudets.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Mercantaler said to him, you know, I can get you-- I can keep you in jail.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father looked at him and he said, Dr.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Mercantaler, after Buchenwald, there is nothing-- nothing you can threaten me with.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Mercantaler somehow told him at the end of these interrogations that you and I-- saying to my father-- have crossed swords with great bravery, somehow respecting.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one of the nice things that happened after I got out of service, there was an article in the newspaper, British intelligence looking for evidence that Dr.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Mercantaler had been member of the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I wrote to Captain Dane of British military intelligence and told him that not only did I have proof positive, but I was in counterintelligence, and I was-- that was my specialty, and that there was no doubt in my mind that many, many times I had gotten a phone call from them when he answered Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I had the [NON-ENGLISH] to find out later on that Dr.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Mercantaler was put in jail again after my affidavit arrived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he died in jail.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I was still at Buchenwald, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he got-- ultimately he got out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know where he had gone, where they had taken him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, there were so many concerns that you didn't know how to sort them out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you just had to take every day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I told in the story that the only thing that I think made my father and me survive was the thought of Mrs.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hamilton, that there was this woman in America.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
